PrecisAppointment of FRÉDÉRIC KIEFFER, of Saint-Lazare, Quebec, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Quebec, as a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Daniel Audet, who has resigned.
